# Apple Silicon (macOS ARM): linux/arm64 matches GitHub-hosted ubuntu-latest on arm runners.
# Smaller image than full-latest (faster first pull). Override with: act -P ubuntu-latest=...
-P ubuntu-latest=catthehacker/ubuntu:act-latest
--container-architecture linux/arm64
#
# If something only passes on x86 GitHub runners, try emulated amd64 (slower):
#   act --container-architecture linux/amd64
